{"id":"9934","title":"Banana 🍌 Cashew Smoothie 🥤 | Summer treats🌞","timestamp":"Tue, 23 Jul 2019 18:30:57 +0000","link":"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2019/07/23/banana-%f0%9f%8d%8c-cashew-smoothie-%f0%9f%a5%a4-summer-treats%f0%9f%8c%9e/","content":"<b>Milkshake recipe : Banana Cashew Smoothie </b>\n\n<b>Servings: 1</b>\n\n<b>Duration: 5 minutes </b>\n\nAn easy, wholesome and healthier drink or as a quick fulfilling breakfast to go with banana cashew smoothie. It’s very creamy, smooth texture and a smart way to sneak the fresh, natural fruit and homemade smoothie 🍌\n\nA must try recipe because it’s full of goodness and  anybody can make it. I haven’t added ice cubes in it because I used chilled milk, if you wish you can use 2-3 ice cubes. Smoothies can be prepared with veggies, fruit, honey and either dairy or dairy-free.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-9940\" src=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/img_9362.jpg\" alt=\"img_9362\" width=\"3072\" height=\"3072\" />\n\nToday, I prepared a delicious dairy smoothie it’s a combination of banana, cashew nuts, milk and flaxseed powder which has more healthy benefits.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-9943\" src=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/f8f2f50a-6a49-4bba-ba36-13c3d1fe8b91-2909-000002808310ba22.jpg\" alt=\"f8f2f50a-6a49-4bba-ba36-13c3d1fe8b91-2909-000002808310ba22\" width=\"850\" height=\"638\" />\n\n<b>Ingredients:</b>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Riped Banana - 1 - Peeled off and chopped</li>\n\t<li>Whole Cashew Nuts - 10 - soaked in water for 10 minutes</li>\n\t<li>Chilled milk - 300 ml</li>\n\t<li>Flaxseed powder - 1/2 Tb sp</li>\n\t<li>Granulated sugar - 1/2 tb sp ( you can use honey or maple syrup instead )</li>\n\t<li>Chia seeds - 1/2 teaspoon - to garnish</li>\n</ul>\n<b>Procedure:</b>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Add in all ingredients in juicer except chia seeds</li>\n\t<li>Blend till smooth consistency</li>\n\t<li>Pour in serving glass and garnish with chia seeds and chopped banana 🙂</li>\n\t<li>Serve immediately, I’m sure you all love it 😍</li>\n\t<li>Happy cooking and Have a wonderful day 🥤</li>\n</ul>\n<b>Step by step process shown below with pictures:</b>\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-9941\" src=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.files.wordpress.com/2019/07/img_9360.jpg\" alt=\"img_9360\" width=\"3072\" height=\"3072\" />\n\n<b>Checkout other Milkshake Recipes:</b>\n<ul>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2018/06/02/mango-banana-%f0%9f%8d%8c-smoothie-%f0%9f%8d%af-healthy-diet/\">Mango Banana </a><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2018/06/02/mango-banana-%f0%9f%8d%8c-smoothie-%f0%9f%8d%af-healthy-diet/\">🍌</a><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2018/06/02/mango-banana-%f0%9f%8d%8c-smoothie-%f0%9f%8d%af-healthy-diet/\"> Smoothie </a><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2018/06/02/mango-banana-%f0%9f%8d%8c-smoothie-%f0%9f%8d%af-healthy-diet/\">🍯</a><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2018/06/02/mango-banana-%f0%9f%8d%8c-smoothie-%f0%9f%8d%af-healthy-diet/\">| Healthy Diet</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2017/12/04/carrot-%f0%9f%a5%95-smoothie-cucumber-salad-%f0%9f%a5%92-healthy-juice-healthy-diet-%f0%9f%99%82/\">Carrot </a><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2017/12/04/carrot-%f0%9f%a5%95-smoothie-cucumber-salad-%f0%9f%a5%92-healthy-juice-healthy-diet-%f0%9f%99%82/\">🥕</a><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2017/12/04/carrot-%f0%9f%a5%95-smoothie-cucumber-salad-%f0%9f%a5%92-healthy-juice-healthy-diet-%f0%9f%99%82/\"> Smoothie &amp; Cucumber salad </a><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2017/12/04/carrot-%f0%9f%a5%95-smoothie-cucumber-salad-%f0%9f%a5%92-healthy-juice-healthy-diet-%f0%9f%99%82/\">🥒</a><a href=\"https://ramyarecipesblog.wordpress.com/2017/12/04/carrot-%f0%9f%a5%95-smoothie-cucumber-salad-%f0%9f%a5%92-healthy-juice-healthy-diet-%f0%9f%99%82/\"> || Healthy juice 